{"tid":899203,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗：我叫希古恩冷靜啲","createTime":"2018-11-12T08:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T10:49:47.000Z","uid":153600,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee8417e50199c76f03afaeb4ffff212607062d6","tid":899203,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=F77gZwdEA7vBqSzj0okTBzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=94802d7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】祖雲達斯球星基斯坦奴朗拿度向外透露在敵將希古恩領紅牌時，對人家所說的話。<br />\n<br />\n「我叫他冷靜，因為他可能會蒙受更大的懲罰。」基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）在祖雲達斯周日意甲傳統大戰贏AC米蘭2:0後，接受天空體育訪問時說。<br />\n<br />\n倒戈鬥祖雲達斯的AC米蘭前鋒希古恩（Gonzalo Higuain），是役上半場主射12碼中柱不入，下半場更領紅牌被逐，他之後反應甚大，一度不願離場。C朗繼續為對方美言幾句：「他沒有太多動作，他因為輸波而暴躁，這是可以理解的，而我希望他不會受到太嚴重的懲罰。」<br />\n<br />\n兩名前皇家馬德里前鋒甚具淵源，一直有指因為C朗加盟，才令祖雲達斯決定外借希古恩。C朗在這場比賽表現不俗，終一洗之前5次作客聖西路顆粒無收的頹風。"},{"pid":"18344e4494dc747fb4200ecdc57d96952317a912","tid":899203,"uid":131369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856acce57c894de4ce835ba6480202b72dab2b41","tid":899203,"uid":12169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"禾朗真係耶穌再世"},{"pid":"a410b4deb3d8434cf20bd6f9efe07a981c3013e2","tid":899203,"uid":69568,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"叫咗你冷靜D㗎啦"},{"pid":"a0afab7f1f22e868567c0795548be6f43ef6630b","tid":899203,"uid":53855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a410b4deb3d8434cf20bd6f9efe07a981c3013e2","tid":899203,"uid":69568,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"叫咗你冷靜D㗎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:53:16.000Z","msg":"就係因為你唔冷靜"},{"pid":"fb34c7b31fe3ea21f3e6e26d695891300b029a82","tid":899203,"uid":216975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"人地以為自己係班馬軍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c87a4889a6809d343d1b95e6d39d1bff20ecff","tid":899203,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做場戲比自己落台姐<br />\n唔係就比人話送分比自己隊"},{"pid":"cad5a68788c3c5de3236e958b8d6a25a7d7735bc","tid":899203,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:46:25.000Z","msg":"牙朗希古恩爭食.gif"},{"pid":"8450a5d8db5fafa77d755c3c773080d3ba46890a","tid":899203,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"雞朗雞姦條女果時有無冷靜下"}]}